    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "It seems like the error is gone when using `DynamicWidgets` component:\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n<InstantSearchNext\r\n  routing\r\n  indexName='queryIndex'\r\n  searchClient={searchClient}\r\n>\r\n  <Configure ruleContexts={[]} />\r\n\r\n  <DynamicWidgets>\r\n    <Panel header='Brands'>\r\n      <RefinementList\r\n        attribute='brand'\r\n        searchablePlaceholder='Search brands'\r\n        searchable={true}\r\n        showMore={true}\r\n      />\r\n    </Panel>\r\n  </DynamicWidgets>\r\n\r\n  <SearchBox />\r\n  <Hits />\r\n</InstantSearchNext>\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever, by adding `DynamicWidgets` component I'm not able to see `RefinementList` components rendered on the web.",
